{"tid":1769598,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：前日講完「傳媒有自由」 林鄭即禁蘋果立場採訪 - 李八方","createTime":"2019-12-05T03:41:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T04:03:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"91fd1b1cca85f5d76c14a65ac62ec98bbf056cf1","tid":1769598,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T03:41:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191205/L3ZYDNAHKAQJMW2PYTU4JXPRRY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191205%2FL3ZYDNAHKAQJMW2PYTU4JXPRRY%2F&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1e35V8GO7j56WmnfPW9WRM38%3D&h=4e99a98c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191205%2FL3ZYDNAHKAQJMW2PYTU4JXPRRY%2F&h=b981ad19\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191205/L3ZYDNAHKAQJMW2PYTU4JXPRRY/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：前日講完「傳媒有自由」<br />\n林鄭即禁蘋果立場採訪 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥前日大大聲反駁美國《香港人權與民主法案》，話「究竟香港嘅市民喺邊方面嘅自由受到磨損呢？我哋有傳媒採訪自由&hellip;&hellip;」一日後佢出席「國家憲法日」講座，點知《蘋果》記者就親身領略到，林鄭口中嘅「我哋」同「自由」，好多人原來都係無份嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191205/large/1575476793_6096.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191205%2Flarge%2F1575476793_6096.jpg&h=0bc9360c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《蘋果》、《立場新聞》記者被拒採訪「國家憲法日」座談會。 夏家朗攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n毛孟靜嘲自摑嘴巴<br />\n<br />\n「國家憲法日」講座由勵進教育中心舉辦，中心理事會主席係全國人大常委范徐麗泰，嘉賓包括林鄭同各位司長，仲有中聯辦主任王志民、基本法委員會委員韓大元。《蘋果》記者梗係晨早去霸位啦，但係想登記入場嘅時候，就見登記表上面早就列明只有指定幾家傳媒至可以入場。<br />\n<br />\n據記者所見，被欽點嘅除咗《文匯報》、《大公報》，仲有《南華早報》、《星島日報》、《明報》、《香港01》。《蘋果》同網媒《立場新聞》都因榜上無名而被拒入場採訪，只可以在會場外面企。<br />\n<br />\n曾經做過記者嘅議會陣線毛孟靜都睇唔過眼，大鬧林鄭自摑嘴巴、自我撕下最偽善嘅面具。佢認為講座顯然係官方場合，只容許一啲「友善傳媒」採訪，係剝奪公眾知情權，篩選傳媒嘅做法亦係政治報復，脫離文明社會底線，令到香港越嚟越大陸化。<br />\n<br />\n李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191205/large/1575476792_bbb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191205%2Flarge%2F1575476792_bbb6.jpg&h=53dec8f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ad68b60fe101570a9b0150d464c5dcbbcd4aae8","tid":1769598,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T04:03:01.000Z","msg":"英國美國加拿大都攻擊緊中國<br />\n但啲tweets無人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Rt + like + reply</span></span><br />\n<br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1e35V8GO7j56WmnfPW9WRM38%3D&h=52c7e002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">/task2</span></span> 攞任務"}]}